  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779220/extras/152c1b60ca6b9c329a553712743894af.poster.avif?t=1709312543\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779220/extras/152c1b60ca6b9c329a553712743894af.webm?t=1709312543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779220/extras/152c1b60ca6b9c329a553712743894af.mp4?t=1709312543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Play as Guano, a dumb seagull that has a lot on his shoulders! While the protectors of the Pohemeda Islands, the Three Grand Masters, are neutralized, you’re the only hope to rescue your home. Food Inc., an evil and polluting megacorporation, seems to have set its mind on destroying every natural aspect of your archipelago. Get strong enough to stop Food Inc. before their garbage overtakes the islands!<br><br>Your mission, should you choose to accept it, is to wreak havoc in the Food Inc. installations, by pooping, screaming and stealing the food of tourists attracted by the corp and its leisure-filled resort. Use the stolen food to feed the Grand Masters, restore their strength  and acquire their powers through a very sacred ritual: Regurgitation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779220/extras/c0c8d2b6883eb2f7d22d324592cfbd74.poster.avif?t=1709312543\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779220/extras/c0c8d2b6883eb2f7d22d324592cfbd74.webm?t=1709312543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779220/extras/c0c8d2b6883eb2f7d22d324592cfbd74.mp4?t=1709312543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fly at incredible speeds in a stimulating open-world, populated by goofy characters! Friends or enemies? Race against them through breathtaking landmarks to discover new powers!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779220/extras/ccf42422bf66313252567fef9faf36f5.poster.avif?t=1709312543\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779220/extras/ccf42422bf66313252567fef9faf36f5.webm?t=1709312543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779220/extras/ccf42422bf66313252567fef9faf36f5.mp4?t=1709312543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Save the Pohemeda Islands from Food Inc, a megacorporation polluting the heavenly archipelago.  Get help from three powerful Grand Masters to succeed in your quest.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779220/extras/a02b2bd7c9045124935dce881ef6eddc.poster.avif?t=1709312543\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779220/extras/a02b2bd7c9045124935dce881ef6eddc.webm?t=1709312543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779220/extras/a02b2bd7c9045124935dce881ef6eddc.mp4?t=1709312543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Finally get the chance to drop a dookie on those pesky tourists! Yell at Food Inc. employees until they go flying! Steal their food just like they stole your land!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779220/extras/152c1b60ca6b9c329a553712743894af.poster.avif?t=1709312543\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779220/extras/152c1b60ca6b9c329a553712743894af.webm?t=1709312543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779220/extras/152c1b60ca6b9c329a553712743894af.mp4?t=1709312543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Play as Guano, a dumb seagull that has a lot on his shoulders! While the protectors of the Pohemeda Islands, the Three Grand Masters, are neutralized, you’re the only hope to rescue your home. Food Inc., an evil and polluting megacorporation, seems to have set its mind on destroying every natural aspect of your archipelago. Get strong enough to stop Food Inc. before their garbage overtakes the islands!<br><br>Your mission, should you choose to accept it, is to wreak havoc in the Food Inc. installations, by pooping, screaming and stealing the food of tourists attracted by the corp and its leisure-filled resort. Use the stolen food to feed the Grand Masters, restore their strength  and acquire their powers through a very sacred ritual: Regurgitation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779220/extras/c0c8d2b6883eb2f7d22d324592cfbd74.poster.avif?t=1709312543\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779220/extras/c0c8d2b6883eb2f7d22d324592cfbd74.webm?t=1709312543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779220/extras/c0c8d2b6883eb2f7d22d324592cfbd74.mp4?t=1709312543\" type=